>> serves: 6

Heat a #large skillet{} over medium heat and add 3 Tbsp @olive oil{3%Tbsp} and the @broccoli florets{6%cups}.

Cook for ~{5%minutes}, then add the @peas{3%cups}. Season with @salt{} and @pepper{} and cook for 2 to ~{3%minutes} more.

Pour veggies into a #bowl{} and cool for ~{10%minutes}. Add @chickpeas{1%15-oz can}, @crumbled feta{3/4%cup}, @lemon zest{1%tsp}, @lemon juice{1/2%lemon}, and @olive oil{1%tsp}.
